# Checkbox — Styles

CSS file: `@acko/css/checkbox.css`

## CSS Classes

### Base
- `.acko-checkbox` — inline-flex, items-start, `gap: var(--scale-12)`, cursor-pointer, select-none
- `.acko-checkbox-native` — visually hidden native input
- `.acko-checkbox-box` — custom box with border `--color-control-border-selector`, bg `--color-card-bg`

### Sizes (via `.acko-checkbox-{size}`)
| Size | Box | Icon SVG | Label font |
|------|-----|----------|------------|
| sm | `--scale-16`, radius-sm | `--scale-10` | `--font-body-sm-size` |
| md | `--scale-20`, radius-md | `--scale-12` | `--font-body-md-size` |
| lg | `--scale-24`, radius-md | `--font-body-sm-size` | `--font-body-lg-size` |

### States

| State | Border | Background | Icon |
|-------|--------|-----------|------|
| Unchecked | `--color-control-border-selector` | `--color-card-bg` | none |
| Checked (`.acko-checkbox-checked`) | `--color-primary` | `--color-primary` | `--color-on-primary` checkmark |
| Indeterminate (`.acko-checkbox-indeterminate`) | `--color-primary` | `--color-primary` | `--color-on-primary` minus |
| Hover unchecked | `--color-primary-muted` | `--color-primary-subtle` | none |
| Hover checked | `--color-primary-hover` | `--color-primary-hover` | `--color-on-primary` checkmark |
| Focus | `--color-primary` + `0 0 0 3px var(--color-primary-ring)` | — | — |
| Disabled unchecked | `--color-border-subtle` | `--color-surface-raised` | none |
| Disabled checked | `--color-disabled-border` | `--color-disabled-bg` | `--color-disabled-text` |
| Error (`.acko-checkbox-error`) | `--color-error` | `--color-card-bg` | none |

## Animations

### Checked Bounce
When checked, the box plays `acko-checkbox-bounce` 300ms cubic-bezier(0.34, 1.56, 0.64, 1):
- 0% → scale(1), 40% → scale(0.88), 70% → scale(1.08), 100% → scale(1)
- Disabled checked: `animation: none`

### Line-Draw Tick (bottom-to-top)
SVG check path uses `stroke-dasharray: 30` / `stroke-dashoffset` animation:
- Unchecked: `stroke-dashoffset: -30` (hidden, negative value reverses draw direction)
- Checked (`.acko-checkbox-icon-visible svg path`): `stroke-dashoffset: 0`, transition 300ms ease-out with 80ms delay
- Draws from the short leg (bottom-left) upward to the long leg (top-right)

### Check Icon Pop
- `.acko-checkbox-icon` → `.acko-checkbox-icon-visible`: scale(0.3→1) with spring easing `cubic-bezier(0.34, 1.56, 0.64, 1)`, opacity 0→1

### Error Shake
Error state box plays `acko-checkbox-shake` 300ms ease-out:
- Horizontal shake: translateX ±3px then ±2px

## Box Transition
`background-color 150ms ease, border-color 150ms ease, box-shadow 150ms ease, transform 200ms cubic-bezier(0.34, 1.56, 0.64, 1)`

## Labels
- `.acko-checkbox-label-text` — `--color-text-default`, line-height 1.4
- `.acko-checkbox-description` — `--font-caption-size`, `--color-text-secondary`
- Disabled: both use `--color-text-disabled`
